public static long solve(long[] piles) {
    Arrays.sort(piles);
    int n = piles.length;
    long total = 0;
    int index = n - 2;
    for (int i = 0; i < n / 3; i++) {
        total += piles[index];
        index -= 2;
    }
    return total;
}
```

### Explanation
